  "content": "# M4.2: Graph Relation Wiring Fix\n\n## Problem\n\nThe GraphRAG benchmark showed `graph_expanded: 0-2` across all queries because almost zero graph edges were being wired during ingestion. The full infrastructure was in place (adapter IPC, pipeline aggregation, `wire_pipeline_relations()`), but target file matching failed silently for all cross-file relations.\n",
